To set up printer for PC:

run \\print-sj-6-2
Double click selected printer

In the add printer wizard, select in Manufacturers window "!Cisco Supported"
if you can find it, and then select the correct Printer model on the right
window.  Or, you can click Have Disk button, and in the bottom line select
\\print-sj-6-2\!drivers\installs, then select the right printer model from
the pop up window.


